Lab -2 SRS (Hostel management system)

The system should be used by the hostel secretary, hostel warden, guards, staff and students.

The Hostel Secretary should manage many hostels and see to appointing Wardens.
The Hostel Warden should allocate rooms, respond to complaints, Allocate Resources and collect fees.
The warden should review the attendance as well.
The guards are supposed to patrol in the night, take attendance everyday and guard the gates.
The staff is supposed to clean the hostel and cook the feed.
The student is supposed to occupy the room, eat mess food, apply for leaves and pay the fees
